data.description: Immaculate home close to Dyess AFB in Hampton Hills subdivision. Gorgeous 3 bed 2 bath split-floorplan home is perfect! Beautiful white kitchen with subway tile backsplash, all stainless appliances, PLENTY of counter space, cabinets, and island. Large living area with a decoratively tiled, wood-burning fireplace for family gatherings. Split floorplan has a spacious main bedroom large enough for a desk and furniture. Main bathroom with soaking tub and separate shower. This backyard is stunning with the covered pergola, seating area and utility shed on side of the house! Concrete slab ready for a pool or workshop. Call today to schedule your private showing!
